---
title: Double Herby Chicken & Broccoli Couscous Bowl with Dill-Parsley Mayonnaise & Chilli Flakes
description: Savour the wholesome goodness of this culinary delight, that’s as good for the body as it is the soul. Perfectly-seasoned, juicy chicken sits atop a bed of fluffy couscous, with plenty of veg tossed through. Sprinkle on a pinch of chilli flakes if your feeling adventurous!
